Package org.opengis.cite.cat30

Class CAT3

java.lang.Object
org.opengis.cite.cat30.CAT3
public class CAT3 extends Object
Contains various constants pertaining to Catalogue 3.0 (HTTP) service interfaces as specified in OGC 12-176r5 and related standards.
See Also:
  • "OGC Catalogue Services 3.0 Specification -- HTTP Protocol Binding, Version 3.0"
